    "attributes": {
        "action": "Hold referendum on paying for the energy crisis: windfall tax or borrowing",
        "additional_details": "Because it is the democratic way to do things, as we have been told about the Brexit referendum.",
        "background": "I think the people of the UK should be allowed to decide how we pay back the money we borrow for easing the energy crisis. \r\n\r\nShould we risk future investment, and tax the oil and gas companies or should we pass the debt on to our children and future generations in the UK?",
